-- Obama rejects any short-term deal on debt ceiling
-- 
-- Mon Jul 11, 2011 11:26am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/07/11/us-usa-debt-stopgap-idUSTRE76A40J20110711

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - President Barack Obama said on Monday that he would refuse to consider a short-term stop gap measure to raise the debt ceiling. 

 "We're going to resolve this and we're going to resolve this for a reasonable period of time." he told a White House press conference. (Editing by  Sandra Maler )